research_municipality_step.notes: Edison Township, NJ operates under a Faulkner Act Mayor-Council form of government. The Mayor and all seven Council Members are elected at-large. Mayor Samip Joshi began his second term on January 1, 2026. Council Members Kelli Dima, Robert Kentos, and Biral Patel were sworn in for terms ending December 31, 2029. Council Members Richard Brescher, Joseph A. Coyle, Ajay Patil, and Asaf Shmuel have terms ending December 31, 2027.
